    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/3ad72c9a5f83b8948094bcf0fb175df3.poster.avif?t=1771490526\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/3ad72c9a5f83b8948094bcf0fb175df3.webm?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/3ad72c9a5f83b8948094bcf0fb175df3.mp4?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这款自动化制作游戏带来了最诱人的特色：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>小型机器人<br></li><li>可视化编程（用于小型机器人）<br></li><li>制作（由小型机器人完成）<br></li><li>一枚火箭（可搭载一台小型机器人）<br></li><li>剧情（见下文）<br></li><li>一颗等待地形改造的冰封行星<br></li><li>其他程序生成的行星（同样全都冰封）</li></ul><br>你降落在一颗冰封的行星上，肩负重要使命：让它适宜居住。为此，你需要采集资源、制作工具、生火、融化冰层、种植树木并产生氧气。预计完成时间：超过9000年。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >或者你可以让机器人替你完成这一切！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/a77bb5f32cdd0fcf0fa415722b0da788.poster.avif?t=1771490526\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/a77bb5f32cdd0fcf0fa415722b0da788.webm?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/a77bb5f32cdd0fcf0fa415722b0da788.mp4?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>登场的是 CraftoMate！你可以用<strong>可视化编程</strong>为它们编写脚本，执行各种任务。<br><br>更重要的是，它们可以用周围的材料进行<strong>组装和升级</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/7681c25c8cb14029076d2eb6e241f445.poster.avif?t=1771490526\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/7681c25c8cb14029076d2eb6e241f445.webm?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724140/extras/7681c25c8cb14029076d2eb6e241f445.mp4?t=1771490526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>更进一步的是：你可以编程让它们去采集并制作这些材料，最终成为一支可持续的劳动力队伍，能够<strong>对整颗行星进行地形改造</strong>。<br><br>只是别忘了偶尔喂喂它们……当然，你也可以把这件事也编程交给它们自己。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们还有程序生成的地图！</h2><br>你可以生成一颗新行星，或与朋友交换你最喜欢的行星——只需分享生成种子。生成器会随机改变资源、建筑和火山的位置，这让同一张地图的每次游玩都略有不同。",
